entries.s_10: He is a scholar of the Tuskens, and needs help recovering some relics. His name is Srimaur. Look for him in Mos Espa.
entries.s_3: Tuskens invading Mos Espa? Wow, I wish I had been there to see that.
entries.s_5: Please, don't let my appearance fool you. I am no Tusken.
entries.s_7: Then why are you dressed as one?
entries.s_8: They fascinate me. You know, now that you have brought it up, I have a friend that could use your help.
